x4freetext: FAST CHOPPER, 2250 RPM(1 TO 19 EV), 6000 RPM
(8 TO 140 EV) AND 11900 RPM(70 TO 1500 EV).
TIME OF FLIGHT, FLIGHT PATH = 21.5 M.
.TOTAL CROSS-SECTION DATA ARE NOT AVAILABLE, CONFIRMED
COMMENT ADAPTED, DATA CORRECTED BY NEW REF.
SINCE IN EACH CHOPPER RUN, INTENSITY WAS NOT HIGHER
THAN 0.6 COUNTS/MIN/CHANNEL, NO CORRECTION FOR THE
DEAD TIME OF TOF ANALYZER WAS DONE.
NO INFORMATION, EXCEPT FOR THE STRENGTH FUNCTION.
BY SUBTRACTION FROM MEASURED TOTAL- AND NEUTRON-WIDTH.
COMMENT ADAPTED, DATA CORRECTED BY NEW REF.
